{"chapter_number":96,"bismillah_pre":true,"revelation_order":1,"revelation_place":"makkah","name_arabic":"العلق","name_complex":"Al-`Alaq","name_simple":"Al-'Alaq","verses_count":19,"pages":[597,597],"meaning":{"text":"The Clot","en":"The Clot","id":"Segumpal Darah"},"verses":[[[1,6107,"96:1","اقْرَأْ بِاسْمِ رَبِّكَ الَّذِي خَلَقَ",["Read in the name of your Lord Who created.","Bacalah dengan (menyebut) nama Tuhanmu yang menciptakan,"],597,30,60,239,null,null],[2,6108,"96:2","خَلَقَ الْإِنسَانَ مِنْ عَلَقٍ",["He created man from a clot.","Dia telah menciptakan manusia dari segumpal darah."],597,30,60,239,null,null],[3,6109,"96:3","اقْرَأْ وَرَبُّكَ الْأَكْرَمُ",["Read and your Lord is Most Honorable,","Bacalah, dan Tuhanmulah Yang Mahamulia,"],597,30,60,239,null,null],[4,6110,"96:4","الَّذِي عَلَّمَ بِالْقَلَمِ",["Who taught (to write) with the pen","Yang mengajar (manusia) dengan pena."],597,30,60,239,null,null],[5,6111,"96:5","عَلَّمَ الْإِنسَانَ مَا لَمْ يَعْلَمْ",["Taught man what he knew not.","Dia mengajarkan manusia apa yang tidak diketahuinya."],597,30,60,239,null,null],[6,6112,"96:6","كَلَّا إِنَّ الْإِنسَانَ لَيَطْغَىٰ",["Nay! man is most surely inordinate,","Sekali-kali tidak! Sungguh, manusia itu benar-benar melampaui batas,"],597,30,60,239,null,null],[7,6113,"96:7","أَن رَّآهُ اسْتَغْنَىٰ",["Because he sees himself free from want.","apabila melihat dirinya serba cukup."],597,30,60,239,null,null],[8,6114,"96:8","إِنَّ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ الرُّجْعَىٰ",["Surely to your Lord is the return.","Sungguh, hanya kepada Tuhanmulah tempat kembali(mu)."],597,30,60,239,null,null],[9,6115,"96:9","أَرَأَيْتَ الَّذِي يَنْهَىٰ",["Have you seen him who forbids","Bagaimana pendapatmu tentang orang yang melarang?"],597,30,60,239,null,null],[10,6116,"96:10","عَبْدًا إِذَا صَلَّىٰ",["A servant when he prays?","seorang hamba ketika dia melaksanakan shalat"],597,30,60,239,null,null],[11,6117,"96:11","أَرَأَيْتَ إِن كَانَ عَلَى الْهُدَىٰ",["Have you considered if he were on the right way,","bagaimana pendapatmu jika dia (yang dilarang shalat itu) berada di atas kebenaran (petunjuk),"],597,30,60,239,null,null],[12,6118,"96:12","أَوْ أَمَرَ بِالتَّقْوَىٰ",["Or enjoined guarding (against evil)?","atau dia menyuruh bertakwa (kepada Allah)?"],597,30,60,239,null,null],[13,6119,"96:13","أَرَأَيْتَ إِن كَذَّبَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ",["Have you considered if he gives the lie to the truth and turns (his) back?","Bagaimana pendapatmu jika dia (yang melarang) itu mendustakan dan berpaling?"],597,30,60,239,null,null],[14,6120,"96:14","أَلَمْ يَعْلَم بِأَنَّ اللَّهَ يَرَىٰ",["Does he not know that Allah does see?","Tidakkah dia mengetahui bahwa sesungguhnya Allah melihat (segala perbuatannya)?"],597,30,60,239,null,null],[15,6121,"96:15","كَلَّا لَئِن لَّمْ يَنتَهِ لَنَسْفَعًا بِالنَّاصِيَةِ",["Nay! if he desist not, We would certainly smite his forehead,","Sekali-kali tidak! Sungguh, jika dia tidak berhenti (berbuat demikian) niscaya Kami tarik ubun-ubunnya, (ke dalam neraka),"],597,30,60,239,null,null],[16,6122,"96:16","نَاصِيَةٍ كَاذِبَةٍ خَاطِئَةٍ",["A lying, sinful forehead.","(yaitu) ubun-ubun orang yang mendustakan dan durhaka."],597,30,60,239,null,null],[17,6123,"96:17","فَلْيَدْعُ نَادِيَهُ",["Then let him summon his council,","Maka biarlah dia memanggil golongannya (untuk menolongnya),"],597,30,60,239,null,null],[18,6124,"96:18","سَنَدْعُ الزَّبَانِيَةَ",["We too would summon the braves of the army.","Kelak Kami akan memanggil Malaikat Zabaniyah, (penyiksa orang-orang yang berdosa),"],597,30,60,239,null,null],[19,6125,"96:19","كَلَّا لَا تُطِعْهُ وَاسْجُدْ وَاقْتَرِب",["Nay! obey him not, and make obeisance and draw nigh (to Allah).","sekali-kali tidak! Janganlah kamu patuh kepadanya; dan sujudlah serta dekatkanlah (dirimu kepada Allah)."],597,30,60,239,"required",14]],[[[1,9,597,"&#xfb7b;","word","اقْرَأْ",["Read","menciptakan"]],[2,9,597,"&#xfb7c;","word","بِاسْمِ",["in (the) name",""]],[3,9,597,"&#xfb7d;","word","رَبِّكَ",["(of) your Lord",""]],[4,9,597,"